  ¡§Pun2 toe7-hng u7 chit8 keng kang-chhiuN2 e5 chhiuN2-tiuN2, si7 chit8 e5 ho2-giah8 lang5, kho2-sioh i u7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 hoan7-tioh8 Siau2-ji5 ba5-pi3 cheng3, ai3 beh chhiaN2 chit8 e5 ka-teng5 kau3-su, thai7-gu7 mui2 geh8 1500 khou. U7 chin-choe7 lang5 khi3 eng3-teng; na7-si7 long2 boe7 hah8 chiah e5 tiau5-kiaN7: Bat im-gak8, bun5-hak8 kap Eng-bun5; ia7 im-gak8 tioh8 oe7-hiau2 siaN-gak8 kap toaN5 kng3-khim5 chiah oe7 eng7-tit.¡¨ 
  Goa2 thiaN liau2, ti7 sim-lai7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 u7 chit8 e5 siaN teh pek goa2 tioh8 khi3 eng3-teng, Siong7-te3 hou7 goa2 u7 chit e5 un-su3, goa2 m7-thang bo5 chin7 sou2 oe7 e5 lai5 hok8-bu7 lang5;ho5-hong3 tui3-hong si7 chit8 e5 chan5-khoat kho2-lin5 e5 lu2-chu2, koh-khah su-iau3 goa2 e5 pang-bang5. Ti7 chit khoan2 su3-beng7 ha7, goa2 long2 bo5 teh siuN7 hit e5 iu-hou7 e5 thai7-gu7. 
  U7 chit8 am3 chiah8-png7 pa2, iok-liok8 8 tiam2 cheng, goa2 chun2-pi7 ho2-se3 lai5 kau3 chit e5 ho2-giah8 lang5 e5 chhu3. Si7 chit8 tong3 chin sui2 e5 iuN5-pang5, thau5-cheng5 e5 tiaN5 chhin-chhiuN7 sio2 kong-hng5, chai chin-choe7 hoe-chhau2; ti7 pun2-toe7 goa2 bo5 koh khoaN3-tioh8 koh-khah ho2 e5 chhu3 lah. Goa2 chhih8 tian7-leng5, bo5 ku2 chit8 e5 lu2-pi7 chhut-lai5 khui-mng5, goa2 theh8 chit8 tiuN beng5-phiN3 hou7 i, koh soat-beng5 lai5-i3, i kio3 goa2 jip8 lai5 lang5-kheh-thiaN che7. Sit8-chai7 si7 chit8 keng toa7 koh sui2 e5 kheh-thiaN; u7 kng3-khim5, tian7-oe7 kap chin ke3-tat8 e5 ge7-sut8 tiau-khek, chng-thaN7 hui-siong5 ko-nga2, tui3 chia e5 pou3-ti3 thang khoaN3 chhut chu2-lang5 si7 siong-tong e5 ho2-giah8. Goa2 tu2-tu2 koan-siong2 kau3 jip8 sin5 e5 si5, chit8 e5 iok 5, 6 chap8 he3 cheng-sin5 chin pa2-moa2 e5 sin-su7 theh8 goa2 e5 beng5-phiN3 chhut-lai5. 
  ¡§Li2 si7 Ong5 Sian-siN?¡¨ i chin kheh-khi3 ka7 goa2 ak-chhiu2, chhiaN2 goa2 che7, koh kong2,¡¨Goa2 siN3 Ng5, sio2-mia5 Khek-seng5, hoan-geng5 li2 kong-lim5.¡¨ 
  ¡§Ng5 Sian-siN, li2 teh bo5-eng5 lai5 chak-cho7 li2 !¡¨ 
