  ¡§Khi2-kam2, khi2-kam2, goa2 m7-si7 kau3-tou5,¡¨ i chhio3-chhio3 kong2. ¡§Ng5 Sian-siN si7 chit keng khek-seng5 hoa3-kang kang-chhiuN2 e5 chhiuN2-tiuN2, thiaN kong2 kui3 kong-si e5 giap8-bu7 put-chi2 hoat-tian2, toa7-toa7 kiong-hi2.¡¨ 
  ¡§To-sia7!¡¨ i chhio3-chhio3 tam3-thau5. 
  ¡§ThiaN kong2 Ng5 Sian-siN ui7-tioh8 giap8-bu7, tiau5-kang khi3 Bi2-kok kho2-chhat.¡¨ 
  ¡§Ouh, m7-si7 tiau5-kang ui7-tioh8 kong-si khi3, si7 in-ui7 nng7 ni5 cheng5 siau2-lu2 hoan7-tioh8 Ba5-pi3 cheng3 chin giam5-tiong7, chhe7 chin-choe7 i-seng bo5 pan7-hoat chiah khi3 Bi2-kok, koh goa2 u7 chit8 e5 kiaN2 ti7 Bi2-kok teh thak8-chheh, sun7-soa3 khi3 ka7 i khoaN3-khoaN3 leh, iah8 chia3 tioh8 chit e5 ki-hoe7 chham-koan hia e5 kang-giap8.¡¨ 
  ¡§Chin kho2-lin5! Leng7 chhian-kim hoan7-tioh8 chit khoan2 piN7-cheng3.¡¨ 
  ¡§Tioh8, Ong5 Sian-siN, li2 si7 beh lai5 eng3-teng siau2-lu2 e5 ka-teng5 kau3-su, si7 bo5?¡¨ 
