  ¡§Si7 an2-choaN2?¡¨¡§U7 e5 si7 si5-kan-siong7 boe7 thang tak8 jit8 lai5; u7 e5 si7 boe7-hiau2 im-gak8; u7 e5 oe7-hiau2 gak8-li2 kap siaN-gak8, m7-ku2 boe7-hiau2 toaN5 kng3-khim5, sou2-i2 long2 boe7 thong-ke3.¡¨ 
  ¡§Goa2 kin-a2-jit8 si7 ui7-tioh8 chit e5 su7 chiah lai5, Ng5 Sian-siN, na7 bo5 khi3-hiam5, goa2 hoaN-hi2 lai5 ka7 lin2 hok8-bu7.¡¨ 
  ¡§Chin to-sia7, na7-si7 goa2 sou2 kong2 chia e5 tiau5-kiaN7 li2 long2 bo5 bun7-toe5 houN3?¡¨ 
