  ¡§Goa2 chai-iaN2 lin2 kau3-hoe7 e5 bok8-su sian-siN e5 hak8-bun7 long2 chin ho2, tek8-piat8 tui3 im-gak8 hong-bin7. TaN oe7 thang tit-tioh8 li2 e5 kong-lim5 chi2-to7 si7 goa2 e5 eng5-heng7.¡¨ 
  ¡§To-sia7, goa2 oe7 chin7 sou2 oe7 e5 lai5 hok8-bu7 leng7 chhian-kim, ia7 chhiaN2 Ng5 Sian-siN i2-au7 to-to hiap8-chou7 pang-bang5.¡¨ 
  ¡§TaN goa2 tioh8 thiaN li2 e5 i3-kian3, koan-he7 si5-kan e5 tou-hap8 kap geh8-hong7 chia e5 tiau5-kiaN7, chhiaN2 li2 kong2.¡¨ 
  ¡§Koan-he7 si5-kan, goa2 oe7 chin7 sou2 oe7 tak8 jit8 lai5.¡¨ Goa2 koh kong2, ¡§Na7-si7 goa2 e5 i3-su3 m7-si7 beh choe3 ka-teng5 kau3-su than3-chiN5; goa2 goan7-i3 bo5 tiau5-kiaN7 lai5 thoe3 leng7 chhian-kim hok8-bu7, sou2-i2 chiN5 e5 su7 chhiaN2 m7-bian2 the5-khi2.¡¨ 
  ¡§Li2 lai5 choe3 goan2 e5 lau7-su goa2 eng-kai tioh8 po3-tap li2.¡¨ Ng5 Sian-siN theng5 chit8-si5-a2 ku2 teh siuN7, jian5-au7 chiah kong2, ¡§Goa2 chai-iaN2 choe3 thoan5-to7 bok8-su e5 lang5 khah bo5 ai3 kong2 chiN5 e5 su7, an2-ni ho2, ki3-jian5 m7 the5-khi2 lan2 chiu7 mai3 kong2-khi2, li2 goa2 long2 theng3 ki5 chu7-iu5.¡¨ 
  ¡§An2-ni, goa2 tui3 au7 le2-pai3 e5 pai3 it khi2, cheng3-sek lai5 siong7-kho3, ho2 bo5?¡¨ 
  ¡§TaN goa2 tioh8 kai3-siau7 siau2-lu2 hou7 li2 sek8-sai7.¡¨ Ng5 Sian-siN sui5-si5 chhih8 ti7 i sin-piN e5 tian7-leng5, chit8 e5 lu2-pi7 chhut-lai5. I tui3 lu2-pi7 kong2, ¡§Khi3 sak sio2-chia2 chhut-lai5, ka7 i kong2 i e5 lau7-su lai5 lah.¡¨ Lu2-pi7 jip8-khi3, Ng5 Sian-siN koh ka7 goa2 kong2, ¡§Goa2 chi2-u7 nng7 e5 kiaN2, toa7 e5 si7 ta-pou e5, hian7-chai7 ti7 Bi2-kok e5 Chicago Tai7-hak8 teh thak8 Kang-teng5-he7, iau2 nng7 ni5 chiah oe7 pit-giap8; chit e5 siau2-lu2 mia5 kio3 Na2-na2, si7 goa2 i5-it e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2, goa2 hui-siong5 thiaN3 i. I e5 hak8-giap8 ia7 chin ho2, bo5 phah-sng3 hoan7-tioh8 chit khoan2 piN7, hou7 goan2 choan5-ke siu7-tioh8 chin toa7 e5 taN2-kek. I e5 lau7-bu2 koh-khah siong-sim, ti3-kau3 ti7 Bi2-kok e5 si5 ia7 phoa3-piN7 to2 ti7 piN7-iN7, hian7-chai7 iau2 tiam3 ti7 New York teh jip8-iN7, goa2 e5 kiaN2 ti7 hia teh chiau3-kou3 i, saN jit8 cheng5 u7 sia2 phoe tng2-lai5 kong2 u7 khah ho2 lah. TaN goa2 ui7-tioh8 bo5 beh hou7 Na2-na2 siN iam3-se3 pi-koan, iong2-kam2 oah8--loh8-khi3,chiah koat-teng7 beh chhiaN2 chit8 ui7 ka-teng5 kau3-su thang kap i choe3-phoaN7, ia7 ke3-siok8 i e5 hak8-giap8. TaN li2 lai5 chin ho2, ng3-bang7 tui3 li2 e5 chi2-to7 oe7 tit kai2-pian3 i e5 pi-koan.¡¨ Kong2 kau3 chia, Na2-na2 i2-keng hou7 lu2-pi7 sak lai5 kheh-thiaN. 
  Goa2 e5 thian ah! Goa2 khoaN3 chit8-e7 hiam2-hiam2 hoah chhut-lai5. Si7 chit8 e5 20 he3 cho2-iu7 hui-siong5 sui2 e5 siau3-lu2; sui-jian5 bo5 hoa3-chong, bak8-chiu kap bin7 piau2-hian7 chin iu-siong, chong2-si7 bin7-heng5 kap sin-chhai5 bo5-lun7 hou7 sim2-mih8 lang5 khoaN3-tioh8, long2 ai3 tit8-tit8 ka7 khoaN3. Goa2 soa3 gang7-gang7, thou2-khui3 Siong7-te3 ui5-ho5 hiah chan5-jim2, hou7 chit khoan2 lu2-chu2 hoan7-tioh8 chit ho7 piN7, it-seng tioh8 che7 tiam3 lun5-i2 nih. 
  Ng5 Sian-siN khoaN3-tioh8 i e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 chhut-lai5, kiaN5 oa2 i e5 sin-khu-piN, aN3-thau5 chim i e5 thau5-hiah8, jian5-au7 kiah8 thau5 tui3 goa2 kong2: ¡§Chit e5 si7 siau2-lu2 Na2-na2,¡¨ chiap loh8-khi3 ka7 Na2-na2 kong2, ¡§Chit ui7 si7 Ong5 Sian-siN, li2 e5 lau7-su, i beh kap li2 choe3-phoaN7, li2 tioh8 ho2-ho2 thiaN i e5 oe7.¡¨ 
  ¡§Ong5 Sian-siN li2 ho2,¡¨ i tui3 goa2 tam3 chit8-e7 thau5, chhui3 lou7-chhut chit8-si5-a2 chhio3-iong5. 
  ¡§Ng5 Sio2-chia2, ng3-bang7 oe7 hou7 li2 khoai3-lok8,¡¨ goa2 ia7 keng3-le2 hoe5-tap. 
  ¡§Kio3 i Na2-na2 chiu7 ho2.¡¨ Ng5 Sian-siN chhio3-chhio3 kong2.¡§ In-ui7 si5-kan bo5 cha2, goa2 tioh8 sit-le2 tng2-lai5 khi3. Au7 le2-pai3 pai3 it cha2-khi2 goa2 chiah lai5.¡¨ 
  ¡§Ong5 Sian-siN, i2-au7 lan2 si7 chit8 ke e5 lang5, sou2-i2 long2 m7-bian2 khu-sok, thang sui5-i3 chhut-jip8.¡¨ Ng5 Sian-siN na2 kong2 na2 sang3 goa2 chhut-lai5. 
