  Goa2 bo5 su7-sian tui3 kau3-hoe7 tiong2-chip kong2; ho5-pit tioh8 teng-kiu5 in e5 i3-kian3. Goa2 khoaN3 che chiu7-si7 thoan5 hok-im, m7-si7 teh choe3 ka-teng5 kau3-su, na7 hap8 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3, ui7 sim2-mih8 su7-su7 tioh8 hou7 in thong-ke3. Goa2 le2-pai3-jit8 chiong chit chan5 su7 po3-ko3 hou7 cheng3 hoe7-iu2 chai-iaN2, chhiaN2 in ui7-tioh8 chit e5 su7 ki5-to2. Bo5 phah-sng3, u7 kui2 e5 lau7 tiong2-chip piau2-si7 hoan2-tui3 kong2, thoan5-to7 lang5 m7-thang an2-ni choe3, kau3-hoe7 kou3 khah ho2-leh chiu7 ho2. Goa2 chhio3-chhio3 tui3 in kong2,¡§Kau3-hoe7 m7-si7 bio7-u2; goa2 ia7 m7-si7 bio7-kong.¡¨ 
  Tui3 an2-ni goa2 cheng3-sek choe3 Na2-na2 e5 su-jin5 e5 kau3-su. Pai3 1 cha2-khi2 goa2 chin cha2 chiu7 lai5 kap i kong2-oe7, tai7-seng ai3 chai-iaN2 i hoat-piN7 e5 keng-ke3. I ka7 goa2 kong2, chit e5 piN7 hut-jian5-kan lai5, hit si5 i ti7 Tai5-lam5 Lu2-tiong teh thak8-chheh, ti7 ko 2 e5 si5, u7 chit8 e5 e7-pou ti7 kiu5-tiuN5 kap tong5-oh8 saN-kap teh phah u2-mou5-kiu5, hut-jian5 kam2-kak kha kiu3-kun khi2-lai5, tng2-lai5 chhu3-nih khai-si2 hoat-jiat8, pe7-bu2 sui5-si5 sang3 i kau3 choe3 chhut-mia5 piN7-iN7 chiu7-i. To2 chhng5 chit8 geh8 au7, e7-poaN3 sin pian3-sui7, i-seng soan-pou3 choat8-bang7. Na7-si7 pe7-bu2 m7-kam-sim, chek-si5 sang3 khi3 Bi2-kok ti7-liau5, chin kho2-sioh, hian7-tai7 e5 i-hak8 iau2-ku2 bo5 hoat-tou7 ban2-hoe5 chit nng7 ki kha khia7 tit8 khi2-lai5. 
  ¡§Ti7 Bi2-kok e5 si5, goa2 hoat-kak ng3-bang7 long2 bo5 lah. Goa2 koat-chi3 beh chu7-sat,chong2-si7 khoaN3 tioh8 pe7-bu2 kap goa2 siang7-khoan2 iu-siong e5 si5, goa2 iu7 put-jim2 si2--khi3. Tek8-piat8, goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 ui7-tioh8 goa2 e5 piN7 ia7 soa3 to2-chhng5 jip8-iN7; hian7-chai7 iau2 ti7 Bi2-kok teh liau5-iong2, goa2 chin put-jim2 sim. Tng2-lai5 chhu3-nih liau2-au7, pa-pa pang3-sak kang-chhiuN2 e5 su7-giap8, eng7 choan5-pou7 e5 si5-kan teh hong7-thai7 goa2; chit e5 ho2 ka-teng5 hou7 goa2 long3-phoa3, chiaN5-choe3 te7-gek8 e5 khoan2-sit, goa2 khah siuN7 ia7 m7-thang chiong goa2 e5 heng7-hok kian3-lip8 ti7 in e5 thong3-khou2 e5 teng2-bin7, sou2-i2 ti7 chit8 am3 koat-sim chu7-sat, bo5 phah-sng3, pa-pa long2 bo5 khun3, teh chu3-i3 goa2; khi3 hou7 i khoaN3--tioh8, tui3 hit jit8 khi2,tiau5-kang chhiaN3 chit8 e5 lu2-pi7 jit8-si5 kap goa2 choe3-phoaN7, siang7-si5 kam3-si7 goa2 e5 heng5-tong7. ¡§Hian7-chai7 goa2 e5 sim-cheng5 si7 si2 pi2 oah8-teh khah ho2!¡¨ Kong2 kau3 chia, i e5 bak8-sai2 i2-keng tih--loh8-lai5. 
  ¡§Ng5 Sio2-chia2, li2 m7-thang ke3-thau5 siong-sim, sui-jian5 si7 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, li2 u7 chiah-nih ho2 e5 khoan5-keng2, chiah-nih thiaN3 li2 e5 pe7-bu2,li2 thang an-sim oah8--loh8-khi3.¡¨ Goa2 chiam7-si5 an2-ni an-ui3 i, goa2 chai-iaN2 si7 goa2 kek-khi2 i e5 siong-sim, sou2-i2 bo5 ai3 koh hou7 i siuN7 khi2 ka-ki7 e5 put-heng7, goa2 chiong oe7-piN3 choan2 tui3 i chhu3-bi7 e5 su7. I sou2 bat e5 ti3-sek chin koaiN5, chin khoah; tek8-piat8 tui3 Bun5-hak8 e5 cho7-ge7 chin ho2, im-gak8 e5 gak8-li2 ia7 bat chin-choe7. Ti7 iau2-be7 hoat piN7 i2-cheng5, u7 ti7 Tai5-lam5 oh8 chit8, nng7 ni5 e5 kng3-khim5, sou2-i2 oe7 tam7-poh8 toaN5 chhut-mia5 e5 gak8-khiok; m7-ku2 tui3 hoat piN7 liau2-au7 soa3 tho2-ia3, chha-put-to pang3 bo5-khi3 lah. Bok8-koai3 Ng5 Sian-siN teng-bou7 e5 tiau5-kiaN7, siong7 iau3-kin2 e5 si7 oe7-hiau2 toaN5 kng3-khim5, in-ui7 i teh siuN7, chi2-u7 im-gak8 chiah oe7 thang hoe5-hok8 Na2-na2 e5 khoai3-lok8. Na7-si7 goa2 khak-sin3, tu5-khi2 im-gak8 i2-goa7, iau2 u7 chit8 hang7 hou7 i oah8 loh8-khi3 e5 i3-chi3, chiu7-si7 poe5-iuN2 i tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 sin3-giong2. Goa2 koat-sim beh tui3 chit e5 lai5 lou2-lek8. 
